812
01:05:10,130 --> 01:05:11,070
Ugh.
啊！

813
01:05:12,170 --> 01:05:13,870
I promise!
我答应你

814
01:05:50,340 --> 01:05:51,270
Come here.
你过来

815
01:05:51,340 --> 01:05:52,600
No! Oh, God!
