Please be quiet.
Shh.
请你安静  嘘...

818
01:05:58,220 --> 01:06:00,240
I'm not going
to hurt you.
我不是要伤你

819
01:06:00,320 --> 01:06:01,980
Just be quiet,
all right?
只要安静就好  可以吗

820
01:06:02,050 --> 01:06:05,080
All right?
I won't hurt you.
好吗   我不会伤你的

821
01:06:05,160 --> 01:06:07,060
Let go of me!
那你就放我走

822
01:06:07,130 --> 01:06:09,150
What are you
trying to do?
你想要干什么

823
01:06:09,230 --> 01:06:11,320
Take a taxi.
我要搭车子

824
01:06:11,400 --> 01:06:14,490
You don't see
any taxis out here, do you?
你有看到任何一辆计程车吗

825
01:06:14,570 --> 01:06:16,000
If you want one,
如果你要搭

826
01:06:16,070 --> 01:06:18,800
