828
01:06:23,980 --> 01:06:26,710
I live just
around the corner.
我住在对面转弯的街口处

829
01:06:29,380 --> 01:06:30,350
Come on.
快跟我来

830
01:06:34,790 --> 01:06:35,910
Come on.
来啊

831
01:06:46,530 --> 01:06:49,470
I thought someone
was following me back there.
我发现有人一直在后面跟踪我

832
01:06:49,530 --> 01:06:50,560
That wasn't me.
不是我

833
01:06:51,970 --> 01:06:53,200
Here we are.
到了

834
01:06:55,340 --> 01:06:57,360
What are you
doing down here?
你怎么会来这里？

835
01:06:57,440 --> 01:07:01,430
I was supposed to meet
some friends, but I got lost.
我来见一个朋友  但我迷路了

836
