Can I have something
to drink?
我可以喝点东西吗

850
01:08:11,350 --> 01:08:12,480
Sure.
当然。

851
01:08:20,930 --> 01:08:23,360
So where are you
from, anyway?
那么你呢从哪里来呢？

852
01:08:23,430 --> 01:08:25,220
Colorado.
科罗拉多州

853
01:08:25,300 --> 01:08:26,390
Sort of.
附近

854
01:08:26,460 --> 01:08:29,260
I had a boyfriend
in California.
我以前交了一个在加州的男友

855
01:08:29,330 --> 01:08:32,960
But...
it didn't work out,
但  我们分手了

856
01:08:33,040 --> 01:08:35,010
so I left.
所以我离开了

857
01:08:38,240 --> 01:08:41,230
You're the first real artist
I've ever met.
你是我遇到第一个搞艺术的

858
01:08:41,310 --> 01:08:42,940
Tell that to my agent.
呵呵  去跟我经纪人说吧

859
01:08:47,520 --> 01:08:49,450
Did he do that?
你身上怎么会有...

860
01:08:55,330 --> 01:08:58,520
I had a run-in
with a bottle of scotch.
我在酒吧跟人打架

861
01:09:09,140 --> 01:09:10,300
I'm sorry.
对不起。

862
01:09:10,370 --> 01:09:12,170
It's all right.
没关系。

863
01:09:15,710 --> 01:09:16,770
I'm sorry.
很遗憾

