Say, did you try
that taxi again?
那  你还要叫车吗

865
01:09:25,290 --> 01:09:27,150
Maybe you should
wait till morning.
也许你可以等到天亮再走

866
01:10:35,360 --> 01:10:36,830
Good morning.
早安

