01:10:48,570 --> 01:10:52,010
Last night was
very important to me.
昨晚对我来说  意义重大

868
01:10:56,710 --> 01:10:57,940
It was a nightmare.
这是一场噩梦

869
01:11:03,090 --> 01:11:04,520
Oh, no, Carola!
喔  不  卡拉

870
01:11:04,590 --> 01:11:06,020
Not you!
不是说你

871
01:11:06,090 --> 01:11:08,920
