<i>Help me!</i>
救我

879
01:11:40,060 --> 01:11:42,220
Oh, look.
听着

880
01:11:42,290 --> 01:11:45,230
I have to go out
for a while.
我要出去一下子

881
01:11:56,910 --> 01:11:58,400
Wait for me.
在这里等我

