01:12:20,600 --> 01:12:22,790
Hey, that's
my friend!
嘿  那是我朋友

883
01:12:22,870 --> 01:12:25,030
That's my friend!
那人是我朋友

884
01:12:25,100 --> 01:12:27,200
I want to go!
让我去看他

885
01:12:29,110 --> 01:12:32,130
Someone cut off
his head!
