907
01:15:08,630 --> 01:15:10,570
Roget?
她姓罗杰?

908
01:15:10,640 --> 01:15:13,070
Victorine Roget?
维多莉亚. 罗杰?

909
01:15:14,640 --> 01:15:16,570
A friend
of a friend?
你朋友的朋友?

910
01:15:18,140 --> 01:15:20,240
Jesus.
老天

911
01:15:20,310 --> 01:15:22,400
I hope you don't mind.
希望你不会介意

912
01:15:22,480 --> 01:15:25,750
Victorine Roget...
维多莉亚. 罗杰...

913
01:15:25,820 --> 01:15:28,750
owns the hottest
gallery downtown.
在市区最红的名画廊

914
01:15:30,320 --> 01:15:32,690
Of course
I don't mind!
我当然不介意

915
01:15:32,760 --> 01:15:34,990
It's what
I've always wanted.
这就是我心所愿

916
01:15:47,770 --> 01:15:51,570
So how does it feel
to be a huge success?
今天办的很成功   你知道吗

917
