01:16:19,900 --> 01:16:21,390
Hey, Maddox.
嗨  梅铎斯

925
01:16:21,470 --> 01:16:22,630
Nice work.
干得不错！

926
01:16:22,710 --> 01:16:23,640
Thanks.
谢谢

927
01:16:23,710 --> 01:16:26,300
I haven't seen you
around, pal.
我好一阵子没看到你了  老兄

928
01:16:27,880 --> 01:16:30,280
Not since
the night Jer died.
自从杰死的那晚之后....

929
01:16:30,350 --> 01:16:31,210
I'm Carola.
我是卡拉

930
01:16:31,280 --> 01:16:34,810
Nice
to meet you.
很高兴认识你

931
01:16:34,890 --> 01:16:35,910
Who's Jer?
谁是杰?

932
01:16:35,990 --> 01:16:38,180
The bartender
at this bar...
他是酒吧的调酒师

933
01:16:38,260 --> 01:16:40,250
He died.
他死了。

934
01:16:40,320 --> 01:16:42,350
In the alley
out back.
就死在酒吧门外

935
01:16:42,430 --> 01:16:45,020
Come on. Let's go.
我们走吧

936
01:16:45,100 --> 01:16:47,690
Hey, you know
something, don't you?
你知道发生了什么事  对吧

937
01:16:47,770 --> 01:16:49,200
Just sober up, Maddox,
你别搅和  梅铎斯

938
01:16:49,270 --> 01:16:51,860
before someone puts
a match to your breath.
不然我等等揍你

939
01:16:51,940 --> 01:16:53,030
Preston.
普林斯顿

940
01:16:53,100 --> 01:16:56,040
I told the cops
everything I knew,
警察已经盘问过我了

941
01:16:56,110 --> 01:16:57,540
which is
exactly nothing.
我根本不知道发生了什么

942
01:16:57,610 --> 01:16:59,200
Come on.
走吧

943
01:17:17,290 --> 01:17:20,230
<i>Promise forever.</i>
承诺是永远的

944
01:17:24,800 --> 01:17:28,240
